title: D.I.Y. or Die: How to Survive as an Independent Artist
description:
D.I.Y. or Die: How to Survive as an Independent Artist is a low-budget documentary film released by Music Video Distributors in 2002. The film is a celebration of the underdog and deals with why artists do what they do, regardless of a continuous paycheck. - Wikipedia

Links: 
- http://www.diyordie.org/ (official site)
- http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D.I.Y._or_Die:_How_to_Survive_as_an_Independent_Artist

This is a full DVD rip, including all extras. A scanned version of the cover is also included.
